snippet.textDisplay: Thank you.  I was looking for a version of this amazing song that i could show my 92 year old Grandma.  Numb has become my theme song since my dad died, her son.  As much as i love Chester's version, I'm not sure grandma would approve.  But this she will love.  By far the best cover I've ever heard...  💞

snippet.textDisplay: I lost my mom a few months after One More Light came out. I showed her that song on her death bed. She cried harder than I have ever seen. All she said was she's not afraid of dying she's afraid of what she's leaving. Oh shit that made me start crying typing it. I'm sorry you lost your dad. I get it. Hang in there ❤️
